label: uncl9213
comment: Code specifying a type of duty regime.

values.label: Origin subject to EC/EFTA preference
values.comment: Origin of the product is subject to EC/EFTA (European Commission  European Free Trade Association).

values.label: Origin subject to other preference agreement
values.comment: Origin of the product is subject to other preference agreement.

values.label: No preference origin
values.comment: Origin of the product is not subject to any preference.

values.label: Excluded origin
values.comment: Origin of the product is excluded.

values.label: Imposed origin
values.comment: Origin of the product is imposed.
